{
  "texts": [
    "As a result, taking into account global context information and multiscale information is a very effective method.",
    "Yuanfeng Ji [49] et al.",
    "proposed MCTrans, a self-attention transformer module and a cross-attention transformer module.",
    "The self-attention transformer module performs pixel-level context modeling at multiple scales.",
    "To ensure intraclass consistency and interclass discrimination, the cross-attention transformer module is used to learn the corresponding semantic relationship of different categories, that is, the difference between feature expressions of different classes and the connection between feature expressions of different classes."
  ]
}